# SCK   LCD_SCK       PB20
# MOSI  LCD_MOSI      PB19
# MISO  not used      PB18
# RST   LCD_RESET     PC07
# CS    LCD_CS        PB21
# DC    LCD_D_C       PC06
# BKLT  LCD_BACKLIGHT PC05  aka LED_LCD 
